"There," Gatara rumbles as she finishes stacking assorted crates of 
engine components by the door.  "That'll do for the first load."  She 
keys her comm.  "Gatara to base, how are things going there?"

"The girl's all packed," Riekan replies, his voice somewhat distorted 
by static.

"I imagine that took about three cycles," Gatara chuckles.  "We'll be 
over there soon with the first batch of gear - just as soon as this 
bug rigs up the transport."
